column_.text_:
Hah! Got eyes on 'em! Good luck tryin' to outrun the
Grandcypher!
Yikes! We need a pilot!
Here goes nothing!
Heh. Clutch save there.
Well, this is a fine welcome!
All units, move out! Secure the ship and those interlopers!

What the heck! Don't they know it's rude to board without an
invite?
If it's a fight they want, then it's a fight they'll get!
You punks ain't takin' our ship! Never in a million years!
Lyria's coming home with us!

Those zealots are bringin' the heat, but we're gonna smother
'em out.
Whatever happens, we can't lose the shipâ€”for Lyria's sake!

This is such a mess. I'm gonna restore some order around
here.

So they wish to overwhelm us. Then we shall respond in
kind!
Leave these scrubs to me! I'll protect the ship and the crew!

They seem well-trained. However, it won't save them from
my flames.
The best way to repel a surprise attack is with force.

How dare they board without permission! I shall take care of
this!

Ah, to be spry enough to leap onto ships! But can they fight, I
wonder?
Obstacles exist only to be cut down!

The master of the Eternal Rage Style dares you to meet his
fists!
Thanks for saving me the legwork. Now let's rock and roll!
Nice of you to drop by. We'll be taking Lyria back now.

Oh sure, charge right in, ya dumdums. You reap what you
sow.
Crush them.
Reinforcements from the right!
Man, so relentless. Hold 'em off!
They're tough. Troops, form up!
Booyah! And don't even think about comin' back!
No, wait! Listen!
Whoa... That's not fair...

We knew they were armed, but why does a church have this
much firepower?
This is bad. They're shooting at us!
Oh boy... At this rate, we'll be blown to pieces!
The ether cannons are our only hope! Use them to return fire!

Get your keister on an ether cannon and shoot down that
battleship!

The ship's a sitting duck! Use one of the ether cannons on the
deck and defend us!
Whoa, this is awesome! Pew, pew, pew!
We're still holding up okay! Keep firing back!
Oh no, we're hit! Is it bad?
Come on, Grandcypher, you can ride this out!
Aim for the red turbines! They'll be lightly armored at best!

Not there, there! The glowing part! That's the battleship's
weak spot!

The cannon overheated! You can fire again after it cools down
a bit!
Darn, it broke down again. Gonna need to wait it out.
Uh-oh... Lay off the trigger till the heat dies down.
Ooh yeah! They felt that one!
Don't let up!

Those are homing projectiles! See if you can shoot them
down!
Here comes more of 'em! Fire! Fire!
You took it out! What a shot!
If one of those hits us...
Oh no! This doesn't look good at all...
That was some wicked shooting!
Go get 'em!
Don't rush it. Stay calm, line up your shot, and fire.
How d'ya like them apples!
They're tryin' to ram us! Get us outta here, Rolan!
Too late! They're already here!
Seize the ship and arrest the outsiders!
I don't understand. Why is this church acting so aggressively!

With the ether cannons out of commission, you'll have to
fight in close quarters!
The real problem is the broadside guns on that battleship.

How 'bout takin' the fight to their turf? That'll give our ship
some breathin' room!
Ready, buddy? Let's get wild in here!
Ready, buddy? Let's get wild in here!

We've been breached! Deploy the Droita Balsam! Prepare to
intercept!
Okay, so you're looking for the gun batteriesâ€”
Yeah, we know! We'll get rid of 'em!
Contain the threat! Form a perimeter!
Stop right there!
Capture them at all costs!

Grandcypher's in a world of hurt. We gotta destroy those
guns!
Take this!
That round thingy's gonna blow us up!
Wait a minute, what if we chucked it back at 'em?
Go! Go!
Keep it up!
You almost got it!
It's gonna go!
Yahoo!
Bye-bye gun battery!
It's a big job, but you've got this!
Don't give up!
Hah, bet that got their attention!
Great job!
That's one gun battery down!
They're targeting the guns! Stop them now!

Hell yeah! No more takin' potshots at the Grandcypher for
you.
Now the port guns are down! What in blazes is going on!
Wow, they could finish it off... Can you disable their ship?

Like knock out the power? Then we'll have to sabotage its
power regulator!
Enemies spotted at the stern! Capture them!
Energy output falling. Connect to reserve power and restart.

Red alert! All units report to the stern! Permission to
eliminate on sight!

Power regulator shutting down. To restart, consult the
manualâ€”
Woohoo!
That's impossible... Who are these people?
No time to relax! That ship's about to fall like a stone!
Back to the ramp! It's time to scram!
Abandon ship! All units to your designated lifeboats!
H-h-hot!
Don't stop runnin'!
Would'ja please quit takin' your sweet time? Move it!
This way! Hurry!
Nice. Looks like we're all accounted for.
My poor heart...
There, behind us!
We got incoming!
Hookin' onto us with their anchors? Talk about clingy!

Still can't use the cannons either... but we can't stand here
gawkin'!

Those chains will rip the Grandcypher in half if you don't do
something!
Then we'll have to destroy them! Come on, everyone!
Agh! We got extra passengers!
Get those grapnels off so we can fly away! Come on!

The red ship's gonna get away! Destroy the anchors on the
double!
Step back from the grapnels! Something's not right!
Back up, or you'll be feelin' the pain tomorrow!
Back up, or you'll be feelin' the pain tomorrow!
Keep your distance! Here comes another attack!
They actually destroyed one!

We've lost a tactical anchor. Requesting backup from ship
three.
That's right! Get off our ship!
I knew you could do it! Destroy the other and we're free!
Yikes! They're armed with explosives!
Geez, those losers don't know when to quit!
Ergh! Damn, they're tough!
Operation failed. I repeat, operation has failed.
Fantastic work, everyone! That was exceptional!
How's the ship? Can she still fly?

Sure can. I wish I had a ship as amazing as yours. Now to put
her to the test!
That dang red ship zoomed into the clouds!
We'll lose some visibility in there. Stay on your toes!
Man, I hate bein' popular!
Don't tell meâ€”we flew right into an ambush!
I've had enough. Hey, Eugen! Cannons up yet?
Think we're good! Let's say hi with a bang!
Show them we mean business with some cannon fire!

Watch out for more grapnels too. I don't wanna deal with
that again...
We've come way too far to get shot down now! Blast 'em!

I don't trust myself with this machine, but I can't worry about
that right now!

You bastards won't touch another splinter on the
Grandcypher!

I could take 'em if they were in range of my magic. But I'm
just as deadly with a cannon!
Hehehe... Let me show you kids how it's done!

The stench of burning metal, it triggers awful memories.
Let's end this quickly.

There's something sinister about this cannon. I'm not sure I
can handle it.

Surviving these odds requires a cool head and a competent
trigger finger.

I've popped off practice rounds at the range before, but this
puppy... Damn!

This machine does not sit well with me, but given the
situation, I have no choice.

Hm... These newfangled weapons are actually quite simple to
use.

Forever pure, forever righteous. I do what I must to save a
friend!

A lovely lass is waiting for her rescuers! Now who do I shoot
first?

Is... Is this where I push? I've never used one of these
before...
Fire the cannon, you say? Easy! Non-stop barraaage!
Hoo yeah, destruction at the press of a button! Fire away!

Haven't touched heavy artillery in a while. Let's see if I can
still aim one of these.

Hitting below the belt, huh? Yeah, sounds like something that
church would do.
I will clear the skies.
That's a hit at our four o'clock!
Big hit to the ship at eight o'clock!
Direct hit! Brilliant shooting!

And it took out the one behind it too. That's what we call a
twofer.

The ship to the left is sinking! I can't believe you hit it from
here!

Took the ship behind it down with her too. These cannons
ain't bad.
They got our cannons! We're in deep doo-doo!

We've taken out a ship without using cannons before. We'll
just have to do it again.

This one won't be as easy, but it sure beats gettin' pumped
full o' holes.
It is what it is. Rolan, bring us in!
Roger that! All hands, brace for impact!
That battleship is at full strength. What options do we have?
Not much besides pullin' up close and hoppin' aboard.
But can you get us in? Rolan, it's a big risk.
Yeah, I'll see what I can do. All right! Here we go!

The Grandcypher is in danger. Let's sink the enemy ship real
quick.
What's the hold up? Time's tickin'; we gotta go!
Everybody onto the enemy ship! You know what to do!

C'mon! Stop messin' around, and bust into the bad guys' ship
already!

Right, same drill as before! Destroy the regulator at the back
then make your escape!
Aw yeah! Let's do this thing!
Intruders have come aboard!
Send for backup!
Get payback for ship six!
Why haven't they been captured yet!

The clock is against us. We must destroy the power
regulator!
Fire reported aboard the ship. Maintenance team secure the blaze.

Gun batteries destroyed. The intruders are going after the
energy regulator!
The regulator is under attack! Protect it with your lives!
The ship is losing buoyancy! We're going down!
Warning. Warning.
Fault in ether flow detected. Switch to manual piloting.
Send in the engineers!

Fighting has broken out on deck. Non-combatants, do not go
near that area!
We're going to crash!
Abnormality in regulator detected. Possible fault in ether flow.
They're trying to send us to bottom of the skies!
Done in by a bunch of skyfarers? It can't end like this!
The ship can't take any more damage!
Lights out!
That's it! She's sinking! Now hurry back to the Grandcypher!
Run! Get off the ship!
Faster, you guys, faster!
There's no escape! We're doomed!
Ahhh!
Phew... That was too close for comfort...
Danger at ten o'clock! Brace! Brace!
This ain't funny, damn it!
Everybody, hold on tight to something!
Aw, son of aâ€”Ether cannon's down!
Heads up, you guys! We're being boarded!
You'll get yours, outsiders!
This is for messing with Avia!
Charge!
You'll never defeat us!

That ship's going to drag us down with it if we can't pull away
somehow. Any good ideas?
Destroying the engine seems effective enough!
Actually that might be our only option. Can you handle it?
It's as good as done! Besides, I don't feel like crashin' today!
Keep them back!
Capture them at once!
You won't get near the Ameretat!
The shaman is under our protection!
Crap! We lost a gun battery!
Do not let them advance! They must not reach the regulator!
What are you soldiers doing out there! I ordered you to stop them!

What am I supposed to tell General Gallanza? That a few
skyfarers overpowered us?

System function abnormality detected. Loss of buoyancy
and thrust confirmed.
Bingo! That's our cue to hightail it to the Grandcypher!
Lady Lilith... Redeem the skies!

Slide down the deck! You'll drop safely aboard the
Grandcypher!
Ship's gonna sink! We're too late!
Ahhh!
Oh my, wasn't that thrilling?
See, this is why my hair's turnin' white.
Abandon ship! All personnel must immediately follow evacuation procedures!
Fools.
We are the Silver Wolf Corps.
Heh.
All that we do is for salvation.
Get 'em!
May the stars guide us!
You wanna piece?
That's far enough.
Let's dance.
So it comes down to this.
Farewell.
Ain't gettin' past me.
Hmph.
Show me whatcha got!
I lost...
Guh... Lady Lilith...
Damn it...
Ugh...
How did I...
Not like this...
It hurts...
Too strong...
This is a joke!
If only I did more...
We were too weak!
There is no retreat...
I can't believe it.
Why... me...
Arrest those fools!
Hmph. Just try it!
The tables have turned!
Force them back!
Stay in formation!
Damn you!
Move to intercept!
No one can beat the Wolf Corps!
Death is too good for you.
We got 'em!
Pft, what a letdown.
Sit down and shut up.
I pity you people.
You sure gave us trouble.

Now that's some frightening firepower! I'm glad you're on my
team!
What can we say? Those bozos weren't even a challenge!
All right, now to catch that ship! It's showtime, folks!
Who are you!

Who am I? Call me Gallanza! Alpha of the Silver Wolf Corps
and strongest in the land!
You bastard! Watch where you stick that thing!
Who cares about a dumb pile of wood!
You see, all that matters...
Is the last man standing!
At least give me a challenge.
You dumb blockhead! We were so close till you showed up!
We're taking Lyria back, and you can't stop us!

One of that church's top brass, huh? This guy's got a lot to
answer for.

You're with the people that kidnapped Lyria. You'll pay for
what you did!

This ain't the time for a brawl, but I reckon force is all you
understand.

Our precious crewmate needs us right now. It'd be rude to
keep her waiting.
His thirst for battle is overwhelming! Be careful, everyone!
If we are to rescue Lyria, then falling here is not an option!

Fight me if you want, but a White Dragon beats a Silver Wolf
any day!
I shall punish you for laying a hand upon my vassal.

He is a man of great physique, even for a Draph. But is it
merely for show?
Return Lyria to us at once, or face the consequences!

I know a tough guy when I see one, and he's as tough as they
come.
A fight to the death, is it? I accept.
We've got a live one here! Let's duke it out, junior!
Your spear versus mine, huh? Sure. It's your funeral.

Hmph. This man could probably take a whole battleship by
himself.
Psh, big whoop. I could bust him up with my eyes closed.
You don't stand a chance against me, Gallanza.

Hahaha! Impressive. No one's ever made such short work of
my unit before!

I want answers, and you're going to give them to me! Why
did you kidnap Lyria!
Why, you ask?

Because I live to test my might against the strong! Oh, this is
going to be fun!
That's a dumb excuse. Can't stand guys like him.
Let's just knock him flat on his butt!
Ah! It seems we've yet to see the limits of his ferocity.
Let me catch my breath...
His guard is down! Hit 'im hard!

Break time's over! I hope you are ready to truly entertain me
now!
His stamina is frightening, as if it were bottomless.
Are we having fun yet! Gahahaha!

Skilled and crazyâ€”the worst possible combo. Watch
yourselves!
Show me some more of that fury! And I'll return the favor!
Oh crap, he's up to something! Keep your eyes peeled!
Incoming!
Ngh... Got carried away and forgot to pace myself...
Now's our chance! Give 'im a smack down!
Hehe... Ahaha! Go for it... Don't hold back!
He's hurt! Let him have it!
Ooh, I like your energy! I just hope you don't die too quickly!

Nothin' seems to faze him... No lack of confidence
whatsoever.
Because... I'm strongeeer!

Fine! You're the strongest for all I care! Just go down
already!
This guy makes crazy look tame. Never seen anyone like 'im.
He's strong, but every person has their limits!

Dude's a monster. Can't let him keep wreckin' the ship like
this.

What's his problem? It's like fighting pushes everything else
out of his head.

Sure, he's built like a wall, but even walls can come crashin'
down!

I hate to interrupt your guilty little pleasure, but I think you've
had enough.
Is he immortal or something?

His extraordinary strength is undeniable, but we are far from
surrendering!
All righty then! Let's fight till one of us can't move anymore!

It seems tepid flames will simply singe, rather than burn,
your callous exterior.

I'll use every strategy in the book to gain the upper hand.
Think you can stop me?
In the name of justice, my holy sword will cut you down!

That's enough games for one day. I'm sure Lyria is gettin'
antsy.
Let's settle this once and for all.
Oh-hoho! You got talent with the spear there, big man!

Is this guy for real? He's a bigger pain in the ass than
Vaseraga.
Pain makes him feel alive, huh? Can't say I relate.
Yawn. This is boring. Time to stomp this chump.
Good. Then I'll take your life.

Those attacks are hard to avoid! It might be better to buckle
down and guard!

I don't know what I've done to deserve this much fun, but I
don't want it to end!
What's the matter? You like kissing the dirt?
Mm, that was spicy! I like a little zing!
Gwah! Not bad, skyfarers... Not bad at all!
Stop stalling and come hit me!

Well done! I'm still warming up so don't you dare disappoint
me!

Glad you haven't lost the will to fight! There's still fun to be
had!

Hah! Use whatever tactics you want against me as long as
they're not half-assed!
Aw, I broke my toys.
I didn't say you could sleep yet! Let's keep this rolling!
Bahaha! Excellent! This is the most fun we've had in ages!
His spear... It transformed!
We're through!
Storming Death!
Thrilling...
How thrilling!
If I am to fall in this duel...
Then it would have been a life well spent!

I'm inclined to say that you've had quite enough
entertainment.
Another one?
I haven't had a worthy fight in ages! I won't retreat!
Really, you speak like a beast with more impulse than sense.

If you're lying on the ground bereft of life, how will you
explain yourself to our lady?
Point taken. I could use a nice nap.
But as for you!

The next time we meet face-to-face, only one of us will walk
away! It'll be glorious!
Duck!
So that just happened...
Guys?
That lady that was just here disappeared too.
She has quite the talent. Yet another foe to keep in mind.
Rolan! What of the red ship!
Don't you worry. I've got eyes on it.
They're flying towards Mt. Neigelithâ€”
The ol' girl's taken too much damage. Hope she don't fall...
We just gave her a tune-up too!
Don't let us down, Grandcypher.
A snowstorm? Whatever, it's not gonna stop us finding Lyria!

The Grandcypher's lookin' rough, but this ain't her first
rodeo. Let's go!
